#. <section class="sutta" id="sn52.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn52.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 52"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 52"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn52.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Rahogatavagga"
msgstr "1. In Private"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Paṭhamakaṇḍakīsutta → kaṇṭakīsuttaṃ (bj) | kaṇṭakī 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn52.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Paṭhamakaṇḍakīsutta"
msgstr "4. At Thorny Wood (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: kaṇḍakīvane → kaṇṭakīvane (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "sn52.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca anuruddho āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca "
"mahāmoggallāno sākete viharanti kaṇḍakīvane."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerables Anuruddha, Sāriputta, and Mahāmoggallāna were staying "
"near Sāketa, in the Thorny Wood."

msgctxt "sn52.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca mahāmoggallāno sāyanhasamayaṃ "
"paṭisallānā vuṭṭhitā yenāyasmā anuruddho tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmatā anuruddhena saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, Sāriputta and Mahāmoggallāna came out of "
"retreat, went to Anuruddha, and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn52.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they sat down to one "
"side. Sāriputta said to Anuruddha:"

msgctxt "sn52.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"“sekhenāvuso anuruddha, bhikkhunā katame dhammā upasampajja vihātabbā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Anuruddha, what things should a trainee mendicant enter and remain "
"in?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.299"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn52.4:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sekhenāvuso sāriputta, bhikkhunā cattāro satipaṭṭhānā upasampajja vihātabbā."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Sāriputta, a trainee mendicant should enter and remain in the four "
"kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya "
"loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.4"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.5"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.6"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn52.4:2.7"
msgid ""
"sekhenāvuso sāriputta, bhikkhunā ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā upasampajja "
"vihātabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A trainee mendicant should enter and remain in these four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn52.4:2.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
